<view class="page-shell home-page">
  <view class="surface-card hero-card">
    <view class="hero-copy-group">
      <text class="hero-lead serif-title">有些话说出口就后悔，有些话没说出口更后悔。</text>
      <text class="hero-copy">「如果这样回」是一个模拟真实对话的演练场——前任的深夜问候、暗恋对象的突然搭话、领导的咄咄逼人、客户的无理要求……</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-block">
    <view class="section-head">
      <text class="section-title">今晚想聊哪段</text>
      <text class="section-note">3 段推荐场景</text>
    </view>

    <scroll-view scroll-x class="featured-scroll">
      <view class="featured-row">
        <block wx:for="{{featuredScripts}}" wx:key="id">
          <view class="surface-card featured-card" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="handleOpenDetail">
            <view class="opening-bubble opening-bubble--featured">
              <text class="opening-text">{{item.openingLine}}</text>
            </view>
            <text class="featured-copy">{{item.blurb}}</text>
            <view class="card-bottom-row">
              <text class="card-tags meta-line">{{item.meta}}</text>
              <text class="card-unlocked">
                {{item.unlockedEndingIds.length ? '已解锁 ' + item.unlockedEndingIds.length + ' 个结局' : '尚未解锁结局'}}
              </text>
            </view>
          </view>
        </block>
      </view>
    </scroll-view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-block">
    <view class="section-head"></view>
    <scroll-view scroll-x class="category-scroll">
      <view class="pill-row category-row">
        <block wx:for="{{categories}}" wx:key="*this">
          <view
            class="pill {{selectedCategory === item ? 'pill--active' : ''}}"
            data-category="{{item}}"
            bindtap="handleSelectCategory"
          >
            {{item}}
          </view>
        </block>
      </view>
    </scroll-view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-block">
    <view class="section-head">
      <text class="section-title">全部剧本</text>
      <text class="section-note">{{scripts.length}} 个可体验场景</text>
    </view>

    <view class="empty-panel" wx:if="{{isEmpty}}">
      当前分类下还没有可用剧本，先切回其他分类看看。
    </view>

    <block wx:if="{{!isEmpty}}">
      <block wx:for="{{scripts}}" wx:key="id">
        <view class="surface-card list-card" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="handleOpenDetail">
          <view class="list-card-bubble">
            <text class="list-card-opening">{{item.openingLine}}</text>
          </view>
          <text class="list-card-copy">{{item.blurb}}</text>
          <view class="card-bottom-row">
            <text class="card-tags meta-line">{{item.meta}}</text>
            <text class="card-unlocked">
              {{item.unlockedEndingIds.length ? '已解锁 ' + item.unlockedEndingIds.length + ' 个结局' : '尚未解锁结局'}}
            </text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </block>
    </block>
  </view>
</view>
